name: Walking Slow on Sunday Morning
description: Now it's day off, i walk alone around my neighborhood, there is small cafe that always open 24/7, i always noodles and drink orange syrup, yeah that's great combination to have breakfast, there's also a small fruit market besides the street, i usualy bought orange and apple, because the fruit is so clean and fresh. Yeah this is great environment on sunday morning, never miss a single week for this ambience.
